{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a0cbd1c38e","title":"翻译说明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2bfffe3610","index":0,"year":2009,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","name":"超凡领袖的挫败——文化大革命在武汉（中文大学出版社2009年）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"王绍光著，王红绩译，中文大学出版社2009年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"6d60db6d10","name":"王红绩"}]},"publication_details":{"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06d05800b4","type":"paragraph","text":"收集资料·梅隆博士斋文樊学金（MellonDissertationFellowship）和麦克阿瑟国际和平奥安全基金会学术（MacArthurFoundationFellowshipinInternationalPeaceandSecurity），提供了我在1987-1988年和1989年的学费和生活费·在同一时期，康奈耐大学研究生院为我提供了暑期研究摸学金·耶鲁大学A·惠特尼·格里斯沃雨德教师（A.WhitneyGriswoldFacultyAward），为我提供了后期写作和修改的资助。","index":0,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"eba9027db6","type":"paragraph","text":"斯坦利·罗森（StanleyRosen）薰了全部书稿，提出了不少有益的批，我对他表示感谢。","index":1,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"328b2f45d9","type":"paragraph","text":"我非常感激牛津大学出版社及其编辑们对这填研究的大力支持。","index":2,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"3493c4f249","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，我要把感激、钦佩和受感给内子趟利群和女儿王晓曦·内子不催承了繁重的香稿打字任务，而且同我一起分享了写作程中的快乐与辛；而径女儿八个月大时，我便负复留学美国，直到她八戴才得以父女聚。","index":3,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"f8a33b0779","type":"paragraph","text":"王绍光美国康湿狄格州，纽黑文本善的王者]是我，次善者是中央黛校的博士生徐海娜。","index":4,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"edcb2b24aa","type":"paragraph","text":"我作为主]做的工作是：第一，翻了除了第10、11、12三章以外的所有正文和附鹰内容·第二，对自己和次者]所翻的内容连行了害校。","index":5,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"58b1cd420b","type":"paragraph","text":"徐海娜作为次]做的工作，就是翻了本菁正文最后三章：第10、11、12章。","index":6,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"},{"id":"8e06940578","type":"paragraph","text":"王红镇","index":7,"publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e"}],"page":{"id":"d583f941c0","publicationId":"71ca7556-6829-4972-a48e-277e38c6dc02","articleId":"a0cbd1c38e","start":9,"end":9}}}},"__N_SSG":true}